      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "in cadrul pagini de curs \nva vedea fiecare sapt si materialele\nsale",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "in cadrul pagini de curs \nva vedea fiecare sapt si materialele\nsale",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "duMCOuCOnTVy9zOi5RNmN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5833.257894803274,
      "y": -5040.07540036265,
      "width": 384.52193761298895,
      "height": 700,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bHv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1664072909,
      "version": 678,
      "versionNonce": 1967363491,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769586770795,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- basically aici UI ar fi cum este si in moodle la\nnoi\ncand intram la un curs dintr o sapt si poate fi\nretractat sau nu\npentru a vedea materialele. \n- aici pot sa impun profesorului cand creeaza \nun curs sa zica de la ce data pana la ce data\ndureaza cursul respectiv\n\nfunction getDatesInRange(startDate, endDate)\n{\n  const date = new Date(startDate.getTime());\n\n  const dates = [];\n\n  while (date <= endDate) {\n    dates.push(new Date(date));\n    date.setDate(date.getDate() + 1);\n  }\n\n  return dates;\n}\n\nconst d1 = new Date('2022-01-18');\nconst d2 = new Date('2022-01-24');\n\nconsole.log(getDatesInRange(d1, d2));\n\ncu functia asta imi iau un array de date dintre\ncele\ndoua introduse de prof si astfel imi creez\ndinamic sectiunile pe\nsapt cu zilele exacte. :)  () am lasat code\nsnippteul ca sa fie la indemana\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- basically aici UI ar fi cum este si in moodle la noi\ncand intram la un curs dintr o sapt si poate fi retractat sau nu\npentru a vedea materialele. \n- aici pot sa impun profesorului cand creeaza \nun curs sa zica de la ce data pana la ce data dureaza cursul respectiv\n\nfunction getDatesInRange(startDate, endDate) {\n  const date = new Date(startDate.getTime());\n\n  const dates = [];\n\n  while (date <= endDate) {\n    dates.push(new Date(date));\n    date.setDate(date.getDate() + 1);\n  }\n\n  return dates;\n}\n\nconst d1 = new Date('2022-01-18');\nconst d2 = new Date('2022-01-24');\n\nconsole.log(getDatesInRange(d1, d2));\n\ncu functia asta imi iau un array de date dintre cele\ndoua introduse de prof si astfel imi creez dinamic sectiunile pe\nsapt cu zilele exacte. :)  () am lasat code snippteul ca sa fie la indemana\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
