      "text": "Usefull links:\nhttps://www.altexsoft.com/blog/chroma-pros-\nand-cons/\n(how does rag work ) \n\nhttps://medium.com/data-science-collective/i-\ntried-every-pdf-parser-for-my-chat-app-only-\none-worked-e20613835d27\n \n(parsing logic with fastapi)\n\n\nhttps://medium.com/@divanshSachdeva/title-\na-beginners-guide-to-uploading-and-\nprocessing-pdf-files-with-node-js-\n6f5745b27654\n\n(parsing pdf files in the nodejs backend)\n\nhttps://youtu.be/oAvTd0I0B0E?si=fz2JUG4\nhBHwXvC41\n\n+\n\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/questions/691074\n45/sending-a-nodejs-req-file-to-python-script\n\n(cum sa trimit fisiere de la nodejs in python\nscript) \n\n\nhttps://tech-depth-and-\nbreadth.medium.com/extracting-chunks-from-\npdf-and-storing-in-locally-hosted-chromadb-\nusing-langchain-utilities-as-of-a3b122afbe41\n\n(how to save chunks in chroma db and how\nto retrieve them)\n\nhttps://medium.com/@pierrelouislet/getting-\nstarted-with-chroma-db-a-beginners-tutorial-\n6efa32300902\n\nhttps://towardsdatascience.com/all-you-need-\nto-know-about-vector-databases-and-how-\nto-use-them-to-augment-your-llm-apps-\n596f39adfedb/\n\nhttps://rito.hashnode.dev/installing-chroma-\ndb-locally-querying-personal-data\n\n(how to setup chromadb kinda)\n\nhttps://medium.com/@muhebollah.diu/underst\nanding-multipart-form-data-the-ultimate-\nguide-for-beginners-fd039c04553d\n\n( multipart method of sending files) \n\nhttps://www.datacamp.com/blog/chunking-\nstrategies?utm_cid=19589720821&utm_aid=1\n52984010854&utm_campaign=230119_1-ps-\nother~dsa-tofu~all_2-b2c_3-emea_4-prc_5-\nna_6-na_7-le_8-pdsh-go_9-nb-e_10-na_11-\nna&utm_loc=9197713-&utm_mtd=-\nc&utm_kw=&utm_source=google&utm_medium=\npaid_search&utm_content=ps-other~emea-\nen~dsa~tofu~blog~artificial-\nintelligence&gad_source=1&gad_campaignid=19\n589720821&gclid=Cj0KCQiAhOfLBhCCARIsAJ\nPiopPjCAbxKRVKFztJ1r8oNHRh5IhlnwZbuQXS\nanJ_BvmBo3YAWdAPlpAaAuJREALw_wcB\n\ndiferite metode de chunks",
